      "text": "じゃーん！　どうかな？",
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってますよ。撮影が楽しみです",
      "startTime": 5.3030612309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.8997278373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがと！\nふふ、どんなポーズでも演技でもどんと来ーい！",
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.2289567948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さん、本当に元気だな。あんなにはしゃいで）\n（心配だったけど、いらない心配だったみたいだ）",
      "startTime": 19.2326729419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.5489570301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ撮影が始まるみたい",
      "startTime": 22.5489570301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "応援してます。俺も近くにいますから",
      "startTime": 25.7389798325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.9952088675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。あ、そうだ\n{user}君。ちょっと耳、貸して？",
      "startTime": 32.3301727047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　急にどうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 35.3179752351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.2342044514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "いいからいいから。あのね――",
      "startTime": 38.2342044514,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 41865.7955486,
          "startTime": 80.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5203.398704500003,
          "startTime": 43.4376031559
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、次のポーズは……こうですね",
      "startTime": 44.2042698225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "いい感じですか？　ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 48.2005478542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影……順調だな。それにしても、遙子さん\nさっきの言葉はなんだったんだ……？",
      "startTime": 57.3666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "――私のこと、ちゃんと見ててね？",
      "startTime": 60.4718681655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとになんだったんだろう……\nもちろん仕事だから見るには見るんだけど",
      "startTime": 66.3666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　休憩はまだ大丈夫です\nまだまだ行けますから！",
      "startTime": 73.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "撮影は次のシーンが最後なんですね\n次はどんな感じで……えっ！？",
      "startTime": 78.8356746229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました……やってみます！",
      "startTime": 82.2947859447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？　遙子さん、どうしたんだ？\n顔を真っ赤にして気合いを入れてるけど",
      "startTime": 90.3333307902,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8986.728036900004,
          "startTime": 95.437656566
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9182.40226110001,
          "startTime": 95.6333307902
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終了後",
      "startTime": 94.0909908975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 95.3043231646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね、浜辺の散歩に付き合ってもらっちゃって",
      "startTime": 96.7043226559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.5797875721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "正直に言うとね、最近疲れてたのは本当なの\nだけど、二人で現場に行くのは久しぶりだったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 106.5333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "それも嬉しかったし、撮影前に君と歩き回ったら……\nすっかり元気になっちゃった",
      "startTime": 115.7666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 118.13040514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか今日は、青春出来たなーって気がするわ",
      "startTime": 118.13040514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "青春……ですか？",
      "startTime": 123.033421294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 125.4745254755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "何年も前だけど、君と麻奈ちゃんって一緒に下校して\nそのまま現場に行くことが多かったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 130.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "羨ましいなー、青春だなーって思ってたんだ\n今日は少しだけ、その気分が味わえた気がするの",
      "startTime": 139.8333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 144.0482898314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に思ってたんですね。あの頃は放課後になると\n麻奈に「早く早く！」って急かされて大変でしたけど",
      "startTime": 148.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのも含めて青春、ってことでいいんじゃない？\n今日だって、慌ただしく観光してたんだし",
      "startTime": 157.5999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 161.2515283505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "君ってば走り回ったら顔を真っ赤にしちゃって……\n可愛かったわよ？",
      "startTime": 165.4999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないで下さい\nあ……顔を真っ赤にって言葉で思い出したんですけど",
      "startTime": 169.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 169.6999974568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "撮影の終盤で\nカメラマンさんになんて言われたんですか？",
      "startTime": 175.9333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 178.6641517717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、もう……どこで思い出してるのよ",
      "startTime": 178.6641517717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
